<item>
            <title>[SOLR-657] Replace deprecated calls with the non-deprecated equivalents</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-657</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There are numerous calls to deprecated constructors and methods in the code base. This includes deprecations from Solr itself, Lucene, and Java.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
